        </p>
        <div class="flex gap-4 mt-6">
          <a href="https://linkedin.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="w-9 h-9 border border-smoke flex items-center justify-center text-mist hover:border-gold hover:text-gold transition-colors" aria-label="LinkedIn" style="color:#a8a09b;">
            <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
